lomat-2020-05-05-1.jpg 138w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/sizes/td-list-s-2/thediplomat-2020-05-05-1.jpg 276w" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/sizes/thumbnail/thediplomat-2020-05-05-1.jpg" loading="lazy"></figure><h5>May 05, 2020</h5><h4>COVID-19: Trouble on the China-Russia Border</h4></a></div></div><div class="td-box"><header><h3>Multimedia</h3><i>M</i></header><div class="td-posts"><!-- flag=cache key=td:posts:section:terms_15_16_11394_12376_12377_15426_33352 --><a href="/2020/05/friends-and-enemies-making-sense-of-the-ccps-overseas-political-interference/" class="td-post d-1"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img alt="Friends and Enemies: Making Sense of the CCP&rsquo;s Overseas Political Interference" title="Friends and Enemies: Making Sense of the CCP&rsquo;s Overseas Political Interference" sizes="138px" srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/sizes/thumbnail/thediplomat-ap_18352112027776.jpg 138w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/sizes/td-list-s-2/thediplomat-ap_18352112027776.jpg 276w" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/sizes/thumbnail/thediplomat-ap_18352112027776.jpg" loading="lazy"></figure><h5>May 13, 2020</h5><h4>Friends and Enemies: Making Sense of the CCP’s Overseas Political Interference</h4></a><a href="/2020/05/making-sense-of-vietnams-suspected-covid-19-cyber-espionage-on-china/" class="td-post d-2"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img alt="Making Sense of Vietnam&rsquo;s Suspected COVID&ndash;19 Cyber Espionage on China" title="Making Sense of Vietnam&rsquo;s Suspected COVID&ndash;19 Cyber Espionage on China" sizes="138px" srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/sizes/thumbnail/thediplomat.com-34310443380_138a9d47c9_o.jpg 138w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/sizes/td-list-s-2/thediplomat.com-34310443380_138a9d47c9_o.jpg 276w" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/sizes/thumbnail/